00:22:56,720 --> 00:22:57,321
What a coincidence.

573
00:22:59,280 --> 00:23:01,000
I was wondering why

574
00:23:01,041 --> 00:23:02,881
there was a bike here

575
00:23:02,920 --> 00:23:03,760
every morning.

576
00:23:04,200 --> 00:23:04,920
It was you, huh?

577
00:23:05,881 --> 00:23:06,480
That's not it.

578
00:23:07,401 --> 00:23:08,480
There aren't that many bikes here.

579
00:23:08,561 --> 00:23:09,161
And,

580
00:23:09,240 --> 00:23:10,321
your office is pretty far away.

581
00:23:11,161 --> 00:23:12,361
So, you were following me, huh?

582
00:23:13,041 --> 00:23:14,361
That's not true.

583
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:15,881
I attended a training program
in Shanghai.

584
00:23:16,161 --> 00:23:16,920
And, I saw you

585
00:23:16,960 --> 00:23:17,520
in the subway before.

586
00:23:17,561 --> 00:23:18,440
I just wanted to know

587
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:19,361
where you were...

588
00:23:20,760 --> 00:23:22,440
Thank you. I don't need it.

589
00:23:22,601 --> 00:23:23,161
Okay?

590
00:23:31,161 --> 00:23:31,720
Wait.

591
00:23:33,801 --> 00:23:34,561
Deng Haiyang,

592
00:23:34,601 --> 00:23:35,561
Let's not keep in touch

593
00:23:35,601 --> 00:23:36,960
or meet up again, okay?

594
00:23:40,440 --> 00:23:40,881
Hey.

595
00:23:41,121 --> 00:23:42,440
Can't we just be friends?

596
00:23:43,801 --> 00:23:44,720
Just let me off, okay?

597
00:24:06,601 --> 00:24:07,280
What happened?

598
00:24:08,801 --> 00:24:09,601
Dad and Mom are here.

599
00:24:10,680 --> 00:24:11,801
They saw that Aunty wasn't around.

600
00:24:12,000 --> 00:24:12,881
They wanted to stay here

601
00:24:12,960 --> 00:24:14,121
and take care of the kids
for a few more days.

602
00:24:15,601 --> 00:24:16,401
They said

603
00:24:16,680 --> 00:24:17,720
they wanted to stay here

604
00:24:17,760 --> 00:24:18,680
until you come back.

605
00:24:19,881 --> 00:24:20,960
One or two days are fine.

606
00:24:21,041 --> 00:24:22,000
But I don't know
how to explain it to them

607
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:23,680
if they intend to stay past that period.

608
00:24:24,720 --> 00:24:25,760
I don't want them

609
00:24:25,760 --> 00:24:26,680
to be worried about us

610
00:24:26,680 --> 00:24:28,161
before our conflict is resolved.

611
00:24:30,720 --> 00:24:31,881
How do you intend to resolve it, then?

612
00:24:32,641 --> 00:24:33,321
I don't know.

613
00:24:35,121 --> 00:24:36,601
We can talk about it
after your thesis defense is over.

614
00:24:40,161 --> 00:24:41,401
You want me to head home

615
00:24:41,641 --> 00:24:42,361
and stage an act

616
00:24:42,361 --> 00:24:43,841
in front of Mom and Dad?

617
00:24:45,760 --> 00:24:46,520
Don't you think

618
00:24:46,561 --> 00:24:47,361
we're being pretentious here?

619
00:24:51,200 --> 00:24:51,960
Let me think about it.

620
00:24:55,121 --> 00:24:56,361
I hope you can come back.

621
00:25:06,240 --> 00:25:07,760
The hidden warriors

622
00:25:08,041 --> 00:25:10,440
surrounded the nine-colored deer

623
00:25:10,881 --> 00:25:12,760
and shot arrows one after another.

624
00:25:13,680 --> 00:25:14,841
All of a sudden,

625
00:25:15,161 --> 00:25:16,440
fierce flames

626
00:25:16,480 --> 00:25:18,361
rose around the nine-colored deer.

627
00:25:19,081 --> 00:25:20,280
All of the arrows

628
00:25:20,520 --> 00:25:23,161
were burned down by the flame.

629
00:26:05,321 --> 00:26:06,081
I've captured her.

630
00:26:06,601 --> 00:26:07,321
Stop messing around.

631
00:26:07,440 --> 00:26:07,881
Please.

632
00:26:08,161 --> 00:26:10,000
He's been pretending the entire day.

633
00:26:10,000 --> 00:26:11,121
He even wore white gloves?

634
00:26:11,720 --> 00:26:12,601
He pretended to be my chauffeur.

635
00:26:13,641 --> 00:26:15,401
Actually, he tailed me.

636
00:26:15,680 --> 00:26:16,960
I was there to add to your radiance,

637
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:17,480
you know?

638
00:26:17,480 --> 00:26:18,081
That's enough.

639
00:26:18,240 --> 00:26:19,841
You have your own

640
00:26:20,200 --> 00:26:21,280
personal chauffeur, you know?

641
00:26:21,601 --> 00:26:22,680
Didn't you think

642
00:26:22,881 --> 00:26:24,000
that you were glorious today?

643
00:26:24,480 --> 00:26:25,440
Stop bringing that up.

644
00:26:25,760 --> 00:26:26,760
My legs hurt

645
00:26:26,841 --> 00:26:27,920
from wearing high heels all day long.

646
00:26:28,720 --> 00:26:29,920
Cong and Qi are asleep.

647
00:26:30,000 --> 00:26:30,520
That's right.

648
00:26:30,520 --> 00:26:31,720
How many times have I told you?

649
00:26:32,641 --> 00:26:34,480
High heels aren't meant for me indeed.

650
00:26:34,881 --> 00:26:36,361
Don't blame your high heels.

651
00:26:36,960 --> 00:26:38,200
Your legs hurt from dancing too much

652
00:26:38,240 --> 00:26:39,641
with your old flame, am I right?

653
00:26:39,960 --> 00:26:40,680
Great job.

654
00:26:40,881 --> 00:26:41,920
I'll get you some warm water

655
00:26:41,960 --> 00:26:42,401
to immerse your feet in.

656
00:26:42,401 --> 00:26:43,081
I'll go.

657
00:26:44,240 --> 00:26:45,081
You're tone-deaf.

658
00:26:45,121 --> 00:26:46,240
You're jealous when I dance.

659
00:26:46,280 --> 00:26:47,121
Just sit down.

660
00:26:47,161 --> 00:26:47,680
That's enough.

661
00:26:54,240 --> 00:26:56,081
I finally saw

662
00:26:56,601 --> 00:26:58,601
your mother's old classmate today.

663
00:26:59,200 --> 00:27:00,680
Your mother always told us

664
00:27:00,841 --> 00:27:02,440
how handsome he was, right?

665
00:27:05,401 --> 00:27:07,081
I saw him today.

666
00:27:07,200 --> 00:27:08,161
Listen.

667
00:27:08,440 --> 00:27:09,000
He...

668
00:27:09,680 --> 00:27:11,361
He was truly handsome!

669
00:27:12,720 --> 00:27:14,520
Was that a genuine reaction or not?

670
00:27:14,520 --> 00:27:15,561
I had no idea before I saw him,

671
00:27:15,760 --> 00:27:18,240
but I was shocked when I saw him.

672
00:27:18,561 --> 00:27:19,401
Are you done yet?

673
00:27:19,480 --> 00:27:20,121
I wouldn't have gone there

674
00:27:20,121 --> 00:27:20,960
had I known he looked like this.

675
00:27:21,041 --> 00:27:22,440
There's no need to worry at all.

676
00:27:24,760 --> 00:27:26,081
What's taking you so long?

677
00:27:26,121 --> 00:27:27,081
Are you retrieving it from a well?

678
00:27:27,361 --> 00:27:27,881
Do you know

679
00:27:27,881 --> 00:27:29,081
why he keeps pestering her?

680
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:30,601
Why?

681
00:27:31,801 --> 00:27:32,641
Your mother

682
00:27:32,680 --> 00:27:33,680
thought her old classmate

683
00:27:34,000 --> 00:27:35,440
was devoted to her.

684
00:27:35,561 --> 00:27:36,601
She thought
he couldn't forget about her.

685
00:27:36,920 --> 00:27:38,280
But, listen to me,

686
00:27:38,720 --> 00:27:39,960
he has an ulterior motive.

687
00:27:41,200 --> 00:27:42,081
Tell your daughter why

688
00:27:42,520 --> 00:27:43,720
he keeps pestering you.

689
00:27:45,760 --> 00:27:46,480
Look at her.

690
00:27:46,561 --> 00:27:47,280
What are you laughing at?

691
00:27:47,321 --> 00:27:47,920
Tell her.

692
00:27:48,041 --> 00:27:48,680
Tell her what happened today.

693
00:27:50,801 --> 00:27:52,200
He's in the insurance industry.

694
00:27:56,121 --> 00:27:57,440
Look at how smug you are.

695
00:27:58,321 --> 00:27:59,960
So, is he handsome or not?

696
00:28:00,041 --> 00:28:00,960
How come I didn't get

697
00:28:01,000 --> 00:28:01,720
what Dad meant?

698
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:02,520
He's so handsome.

699
00:28:02,841 --> 00:28:03,641
Tell her how handsome he is.

700
00:28:03,680 --> 00:28:04,361
That's enough.

701
00:28:04,841 --> 00:28:05,480
He hasn't grown an inch

702
00:28:05,720 --> 00:28:07,000
since he graduated from

703
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:08,081
primary school.

704
00:28:12,041 --> 00:28:12,920
You should thank me.

705
00:28:13,440 --> 00:28:14,920
You would've fallen into the trap

706
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:16,161
had I not rescued you today.

707
00:28:16,240 --> 00:28:17,121
That's enough.

708
00:28:18,041 --> 00:28:18,841
I'm back.

709
00:28:20,680 --> 00:28:21,561
My feet are so sore.

710
00:28:21,720 --> 00:28:22,280
Take your foot bath.

711
00:28:23,401 --> 00:28:24,041
Dad, Mom.

712
00:28:24,440 --> 00:28:25,081
You're back.

713
00:28:25,280 --> 00:28:25,881
Gao Ping.

714
00:28:25,920 --> 00:28:26,440
You're back.

715
00:28:26,720 --> 00:28:27,401
I thought Xiang Qian said

716
00:28:27,440 --> 00:28:28,801
you would come back in a few more days.

717
00:28:29,601 --> 00:28:30,841
My meeting ended in advance.

718
00:28:30,881 --> 00:28:31,480
That's why I came back.

719
00:28:32,601 --> 00:28:33,760
Give me the box.

720
00:28:38,161 --> 00:28:38,920
Leave it in there.

721
00:28:38,960 --> 00:28:39,920
I'll organize it later.

722
00:28:44,520 --> 00:28:46,200
You have quite a lot
of meetings lately, huh?

723
00:28:46,601 --> 00:28:48,480
I heard that you had
plenty of meetings in Suzhou.

724
00:28:49,240 --> 00:28:49,601
That's right.

725
00:28:49,641 --> 00:28:51,401
There's a new project
from the institute.

726
00:28:51,520 --> 00:28:52,720
My supervisor is there too.

727
00:28:52,720 --> 00:28:53,401
That's why I have to go.

728
00:28:55,520 --> 00:28:56,280
Gao Ping,

729
00:28:57,041 --> 00:28:58,720
it's good that you're busy.

730
00:28:59,161 --> 00:29:00,920
But you can't just
forget about your family.

731
00:29:02,041 --> 00:29:02,601
You see,

732
00:29:02,720 --> 00:29:03,440
in your family,

733
00:29:04,161 --> 00:29:05,280
Xiang Qian is looking after the two kids

734
00:29:05,920 --> 00:29:06,920
by herself.

735
00:29:07,480 --> 00:29:08,680
When they fell sick,

736
00:29:09,081 --> 00:29:10,200
she panicked,
and everything went to hell.

737
00:29:11,641 --> 00:29:12,401
Last night,

738
00:29:12,440 --> 00:29:14,361
Cong and Qi fell sick.

739
00:29:17,480 --> 00:29:18,321
Don't you know that?

740
00:29:19,121 --> 00:29:19,760
He does.

741
00:29:20,760 --> 00:29:21,240
I do.

742
00:29:21,841 --> 00:29:22,680
Xiang Qian told me

743
00:29:22,680 --> 00:29:23,920
that it wasn't anything major.

744
00:29:23,920 --> 00:29:24,760
That's why I didn't come back.

745
00:29:25,960 --> 00:29:26,480
Dad, Mom,

746
00:29:26,760 --> 00:29:28,081
you guys should rest early.

747
00:29:28,520 --> 00:29:29,280
You just came back.

748
00:29:29,641 --> 00:29:30,361
You should take a bath.

749
00:29:30,561 --> 00:29:30,960
Okay.

750
00:29:31,000 --> 00:29:31,561
Please have a seat.

751
00:29:36,680 --> 00:29:37,480
Did you see that?

752
00:29:38,680 --> 00:29:39,401
Let's go.

753
00:29:39,801 --> 00:29:41,041
I haven't dried my feet yet.

754
00:29:41,121 --> 00:29:42,081
No need for that.

755
00:29:42,760 --> 00:29:43,841
What are you doing?

756
00:29:45,440 --> 00:29:46,641
I'm dripping water all over the floor.

757
00:29:46,680 --> 00:29:47,520
Let's go.

758
00:29:56,601 --> 00:29:58,440
I saw a Porsche on our parking lot.

759
00:30:01,000 --> 00:30:01,960
It's Chai Jin's car.

760
00:30:03,401 --> 00:30:04,920
My car broke down.
It hasn't been repaired yet.

761
00:30:09,041 --> 00:30:10,041
Why didn't you tell me about it?

762
00:30:11,920 --> 00:30:13,561
Are we even keeping in touch these days?

763
00:30:18,841 --> 00:30:19,401
Stop messing around.

764
00:30:19,401 --> 00:30:20,480
What are you doing? Just sleep.

765
00:30:23,000 --> 00:30:23,960
Don't you think

766
00:30:24,680 --> 00:30:26,200
something's off about

767
00:30:26,601 --> 00:30:28,200
Xiang Qian and her husband today?

768
00:30:31,161 --> 00:30:32,240
What do you mean?

769
00:30:33,121 --> 00:30:33,801
Xiang Qian said

770
00:30:33,841 --> 00:30:35,440
Gao Ping loved the children.

771
00:30:35,920 --> 00:30:37,161
He would always buy gifts for them

772
00:30:37,200 --> 00:30:38,480
whenever he came back
from business trips.

773
00:30:38,841 --> 00:30:39,520
At the very worst,

774
00:30:40,081 --> 00:30:41,841
he would buy them a box of snacks.

775
00:30:42,361 --> 00:30:43,280
But did you see it?

776
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:45,440
Gao Ping came back

777
00:30:46,161 --> 00:30:47,361
without buying anything today.

778
00:30:48,680 --> 00:30:49,920
Did he leave it in his luggage

779
00:30:50,000 --> 00:30:50,960
because he forgot?

780
00:30:54,680 --> 00:30:55,561
Xiang Qian said

781
00:30:56,361 --> 00:30:57,401
Gao Ping would be worried

782
00:30:57,401 --> 00:30:58,520
whenever the kids were sick.

783
00:30:59,440 --> 00:31:00,121
But today,

784
00:31:00,121 --> 00:31:01,440
just look at his expression
when he looked at me.

785
00:31:03,000 --> 00:31:04,480
It felt as if he didn't know

786
00:31:04,480 --> 00:31:05,480
that the kids were sick.

787
00:31:06,440 --> 00:31:07,280
Let's analyze it.

788
00:31:08,240 --> 00:31:09,520
Why did Xiang Qian

789
00:31:09,561 --> 00:31:10,321
keep it from him?

790
00:31:11,041 --> 00:31:11,720
Why didn't she

791
00:31:12,480 --> 00:31:13,641
tell us about the real situation?

792
00:31:13,641 --> 00:31:15,161
Maybe she's afraid that it might affect

793
00:31:15,161 --> 00:31:16,121
his work.

794
00:31:16,321 --> 00:31:17,480
She's afraid
that it might stress him out.

795
00:31:17,720 --> 00:31:18,881
Maybe he's under too much pressure.

796
00:31:19,841 --> 00:31:21,720
You're basically saying nothing.

797
00:31:22,361 --> 00:31:23,440
Go to sleep.

798
00:31:23,680 --> 00:31:24,801
The analysis isn't even that hard.

799
00:31:24,881 --> 00:31:25,401
My goodness.

800
00:31:27,121 --> 00:31:28,641
As if you didn't bring that up.

801
00:31:31,680 --> 00:31:32,920
What happened to the kids?

802
00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:36,280
They had acute gastroenteritis.

803
00:31:36,401 --> 00:31:37,801
Maybe it was something bad they ate.

804
00:31:39,280 --> 00:31:40,200
What did you feed them?

805
00:31:43,240 --> 00:31:44,081
They had milk

806
00:31:44,520 --> 00:31:46,321
and sandwich in the morning.

807
00:31:48,801 --> 00:31:49,680
Did you put round ham

808
00:31:49,720 --> 00:31:51,000
in the sandwich?

809
00:31:54,161 --> 00:31:55,200
It was almost expired

810
00:31:55,280 --> 00:31:56,641
when I came upon it a few days ago.

811
00:31:57,041 --> 00:31:58,161
I forgot to remind you to throw it away.

812
00:32:01,520 --> 00:32:03,161
If so, why didn't you
throw it away immediately?

813
00:32:03,321 --> 00:32:04,480
Pay attention to what I said.

814
00:32:04,520 --> 00:32:06,041
I said it was almost expired.

815
00:32:06,081 --> 00:32:07,480
I didn't say that it was expired.

816
00:32:07,641 --> 00:32:09,161
How could I throw it away
when it wasn't expired?

817
00:32:09,601 --> 00:32:10,881
I barely had any time in the morning.

818
00:32:10,920 --> 00:32:11,440
How could I

819
00:32:11,480 --> 00:32:12,601
check every ingredient

820
00:32:12,641 --> 00:32:13,720
and see if they were expired or not?

821
00:32:14,081 --> 00:32:15,601
I've made breakfast so many times.

822
00:32:15,680 --> 00:32:17,000
Why has this
never happened before, then?

823
00:32:17,161 --> 00:32:17,641
That's right.

824
00:32:17,680 --> 00:32:19,041
You were the one
who made breakfast usually.

825
00:32:19,440 --> 00:32:20,200
Raise your volume.

826
00:32:21,081 --> 00:32:22,081
Let Dad and Mom hear it too.

827
00:32:24,601 --> 00:32:25,401
What do you mean by that?

828
00:32:25,561 --> 00:32:25,960
Don't talk.

829
00:32:26,280 --> 00:32:27,480
You're blaming me
for raising my voice now?

830
00:32:28,480 --> 00:32:29,121
What's the matter?

831
00:32:32,760 --> 00:32:33,680
Don't talk.

832
00:32:36,321 --> 00:32:37,161
What was that?

833
00:32:40,240 --> 00:32:40,841
What are you doing?

834
00:32:41,520 --> 00:32:42,440
Come here.

835
00:32:46,720 --> 00:32:47,520
What?

836
00:32:47,841 --> 00:32:49,041
My hearing is terrible.
Hear it on my behalf.

837
00:32:49,440 --> 00:32:49,960
You.

838
00:32:50,240 --> 00:32:51,480
Eavesdrop on them.
My hearing is terrible.

839
00:32:57,161 --> 00:32:57,881
There's nothing.

840
00:33:03,960 --> 00:33:04,720
Dad, you're still awake?

841
00:33:05,280 --> 00:33:05,720
Yeah.

842
00:33:06,960 --> 00:33:07,561
You see, I...

843
00:33:07,641 --> 00:33:08,881
My lower back is aching a little.

844
00:33:14,520 --> 00:33:15,680
Your lower back is aching?

845
00:33:17,881 --> 00:33:19,240
I need to use the restroom.

846
00:33:19,641 --> 00:33:20,240
If so, I...

847
00:33:20,480 --> 00:33:21,720
Let me get you some ointment.

848
00:33:21,841 --> 00:33:22,601
No need for that.

849
00:33:24,881 --> 00:33:26,041
Why aren't you guys asleep yet?

850
00:33:26,401 --> 00:33:26,960
I...

851
00:33:27,121 --> 00:33:28,520
I'm getting some water.
I'll sleep after that.

852
00:33:29,401 --> 00:33:29,920
Alright, then.

853
00:33:30,601 --> 00:33:31,041
Okay.

854
00:33:31,480 --> 00:33:32,041
Are you sure you're fine?

855
00:33:32,161 --> 00:33:33,000
I'm fine.

856
00:33:33,760 --> 00:33:34,440
Do you need my help?

857
00:33:34,601 --> 00:33:35,200
No thanks.

858
00:33:35,561 --> 00:33:36,881
